  "comment": "The H2O TWO is a stimulating lighting fixture designed to bring a dynamic water-like effect to your lighting display. With a bright 120-Watt cool white LED source and 5 Dichroic colors, this fixture creates a mesmerizing simulated water effect that can be projected onto walls, ceilings, or floors. The H2O Two can be used with or without fog and is great for mood or background lighting.\nThis fixture is equipped with two DMX channel modes and may be controlled via DMX, the included IR wireless remote or from the built-in programs, giving you complete control over your lighting setup. The digital DMX display with a 4-button menu makes navigation easy, while the 0-100% dimming (via DMX) manual adjustable zoom and focusing lens allow you to fine-tune the lighting to your exact specifications.\nBuilt to last, the H2O Two features long-life LED source rating of 50,000 hours, and multi-voltage operation (AC 120-240V 50/60Hz). The fixture is fan-cooled and includes a safety loop on the rear panel, ensuring reliable and safe operation. With a power consumption of only 128W (120V) or 125W (220V), the H2O TWO can run all night without the need for a duty cycle.",
